data.description: Gorgeous corner lot single story home in the city of Rialto. 4 Bedrooms and 2 baths. A true gem in the Inland Empire, offering a spacious layout, Walk-in closet in the Master Suite, tile flooring throughout the house, family room with cozy fireplace, upgraded bathrooms, spacious kitchen with granite countertops, inside laundry room, two car garage, new roof and more. Large backyard with cemented patio, lots of plants and fruit trees, fantastic for family gatherings.  This home is located near schools, shopping center, public transportation. It is also accessible to the 210,215 and 10 freeways. Don't miss this opportunity. It will sell fast!
